space\">\r\n<li><em class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-check\"></em> Wechat Official Account Setup;</li>\r\n<li><em class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-check\"></em> Social CRM Solution;</li>\r\n<li><em class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-check\"></em> Digital Marketing Creative and Executive Plan;</li>\r\n<li><em class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-check\"></em>&nbsp;Our Team Young and has the Vigor and Vitality?</li>\r\n<li><em class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-check\"></em>&nbsp;7*24H Supports?</li>\r\n<li><em class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-check\"></em> Public and Private Cloud Solution?</li>\r\n<li><em class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-check\"></em> Built with HTML5, CSS3, Mysql and the latest jQuery version?</li>\r\n<li><em class=\"uk-icon uk-icon-check\"></em> Works with Global and Different Time Zone;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Project Team</h2>\r\n<p>Who are interdisciplinary team with the right mix of skills &amp; PMP to implement the smooth and successful execution of any project, especially in the CRM, Social field and Wechat official account operation.</p>\r\n<p>[widgetkit id=37]</p>\r\n<h2>Account Team</h2>\r\n<p>Who have more than 5 years account executive experience and consultancy with a simple mission: to provide the plans, tools, tactics and tips to service your business.</p>\r\n<p>[widgetkit id=45]</p>\r\n<h2>Marketing Team</h2>\r\n<p>Who can help you get clarity around your business idea, who you serve, and what you can do to get your business in front of your target customers.</p>\r\n<p>[widgetkit id=10]</p>', '', '1', '2', '2011-06-08 11:16:09', '545', '', '2016-10-25 07:00:52', '545', '0', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-06-08 11:16:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', '8', '6', '', '', '1', '32', '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', '0', 'en-GB', ''), ('29', '179', 'Expertise', 'expertise', '<div class=\"uk-grid\" data-uk-grid-margin=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"uk-width-medium-1-2\">\r\n<p class=\"uk-article-lead\">Ejoy Tech is a flexible and professional company to manage your business with Wechat solution. It provides a much improved social CRM experience.</p>\r\n<p>The key feature is the ability to create your very own social CRM system with Wechat popular functions like official account and little APPs. You define what feature is you care about - e.g. push message by group, docking wtih the current CRM system &nbsp;or tracking &amp; Tag the user\'s activities on Wechat. Any combination is imaginable! You bring the requirement, we brings the solution to structure it and make it look good!</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=132&amp;lang=en\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"uk-button\">VIEW WORKS</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"uk-width-medium-1-2 uk-text-center-small\"><a href=\"http://www.yootheme.com/videos/zoo_video_tour.mp4\" data-lightbox=\"width:852;height:480;autoplay:true;\"> <img src=\"images/yootheme/zoo_video_tour.png\" alt=\"Take the video tour on the ZOO!\" width=\"500\" height=\"300\" title=\"Take the video tour on the ZOO!\" /> </a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Apps for every Purpose</h2>\r\n<p>We can provide you with core solution of social CRM, whether you are the group clients with mature CRM system or the brands who want to start new eCRM/sCRM management system. The Chameleon solution are optimized for different situations and types of platform catalogs. It offers a wide range of apps to get you started right away. There is an user center, a coupon catalog, a member card system, an user tags management, an E-shop, an eCSR hotline system and a central control APIs !</p>\r\n<h3>Business Integration</h3>\r\n<p>The core business modules (Cham?on, Digital, SMS express and Think Tank) as a powerful support to core system, make the social CRM more strong to create a better vision of CRM for you By a thriving ecosystem, with new Wechat extensions appearing regularly. It also integrates well with many popular CRM extensions. Besides the Cham?on component itself offers additional modules and plugins. They allow a seamless integration into Wechat new features and provide a richer tool set to create your business success.</p>\r\n<div class=\"uk-grid\" data-uk-grid-margin=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"uk-width-medium-1-1\">\r\n<div class=\"uk-panel uk-panel-box uk-text-center\">\r\n<p><strong>Contact Us.</strong> A flexible and powerful team dedicate to make people enjoy the life. <a href=\"http://www.yootheme.com/zoo\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"uk-button uk-button-primary uk-margin-left\">Download our presentation</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', '1', '2', '2011-05-02 11:47:22', '545', '', '2016-10-25 15:59:47', '545', '0', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2011-05-02 11:47:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"url